of a dangerous and enigmatic billionaire who wants the masks for herself, while discovering these relics contain dark secrets and a power that defies logic. Power that may, in fact, be divine.","name":"Tomb Raider: The Legend of Lara Croft Season 2","name_cn":"古墓丽影 劳拉·克劳馥传奇 第二季","tags":[{"name":"2025","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"网飞","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"WEB","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"冒险","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"古墓丽影 劳拉·克劳馥传奇 第二季"},{"key":"话数","value":"8"},{"key":"放送开始","value":"2025年12月11日"},{"key":"在线播放平台","value":"Netflix"},{"key":"动画制作","value":"Powerhouse Animation Studios"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":4,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":3,"5":0,"6":1,"7":0,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":4.5},"total_episodes":8,"collection":{"on_hold":1,"dropped":3,"wish":2,"collect":6,"doing":2},"id":609143,"eps":8,"meta_tags":[],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},"episodes":[{"airdate":"2025-12-11","name":"No Good Deed","name_cn":"","duration":"24m","desc":"","ep":1,"sort":1,"id":1603186,"subject_id":609143,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":1440},{"airdate":"2025-12-11","name":"Festa de Iemanja","name_cn":"","duration":"25m","desc":"","ep":2,"sort":2,"id":1603187,"subject_id":609143,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":1500},{"airdate":"2025-12-11","name":"Crossroads","name_cn":"","duration":"22m","desc":"","ep":3,"sort":3,"id":1603188,"subject_id":609143,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":1320},{"airdate":"2025-12-11","name":"Slán Abhaile","name_cn":"","duration":"27m","desc":"","ep":4,"sort":4,"id":1603189,"subject_id":609143,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":1620},{"airdate":"2025-12-11","name":"Croft's 6","name_cn":"","duration":"23m","desc":"","ep":5,"sort":5,"id":1603190,"subject_id":609143,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":1380},{"airdate":"2025-12-11","name":"The One Who Kills and Is Thanked for It","name_cn":"","duration":"25m","desc":"","ep":6,"sort":6,"id":1603191,"subject_id":609143,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":1500},{"airdate":"2025-12-11","name":"The Breaking of the Land","name_cn":"","duration":"28m","desc":"","ep":7,"sort":7,"id":1603192,"subject_id":609143,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":1680},{"airdate":"2025-12-11","name":"The Bringer of Death","name_cn":"","duration":"30m","desc":"","ep":8,"sort":8,"id":1603193,"subject_id":609143,"comment":0,"type":0,"disc":0,"duration_seconds":1800}],"updatedAt":"2026-05-01T19:27:43.475Z"},"609175":{"detail":{"date":"2026-04-10","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/a3/31/609175_n2ed9.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/a3/31/609175_n2ed9.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/a3/31/609175_n2ed9.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/a3/31/609175_n2ed9.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/a3/31/609175_n2ed9.jpg"},"summary":"世界级的葡萄酒评论家神咲丰多香辞世后，留下了一批时价超过120亿圆的葡萄酒收藏。\r\n他在遗嘱中表示，只要有谁能将他亲自选出的12瓶伟大的葡萄酒，以及立于其顶点的梦幻逸品「神之雫」，\r\n连同酒名及生产年份全部答对，就将他的遗产全部让渡给那个人。\r\n这场壮大的试炼挑战者，是尽管从小接受葡萄酒的英才教育，却反抗父亲，甚至不曾喝过葡萄酒的丰多香的亲生儿子神咲雫，以及成为丰多香的养子的年轻教主级葡萄酒评论家・远峰一青。\r\n何谓葡萄酒？何谓亲子？又何谓人生？\r\n这场围绕在梦幻的葡萄酒「神之雫」之间的一段复杂而芳醇的战斗，现在即将开始——\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[简介原文]\r\n世界的ワイン評論家・神咲豊多香がこの世を去り、時価120億円を超えるワインコレクションが遺された。その遺言状には、彼が選んだ偉大なる12本のワイン“十二使徒”とその頂点に立つ幻の１本“神の雫” を、銘柄および生産年まで言い当てた者に遺産のすべてを譲り渡すと記されていた。\r\nこの壮大な挑戦に挑むのは、豊多香の実の息子でワインの英才教育を受けながらも父に背き、ワインを口にした経験のない神咲雫と、豊多香と養子縁組を結んだ若きカリスマワイン評論家・遠峰一青の２人。\r\nワインとは、親子とは、人生とはなにか。\r\n幻のワイン“神の雫”を巡り繰る複雑で芳醇な戦いが、今、始まる――","name":"神の雫","name_cn":"神之水滴","tags":[{"name":"2026年4月","count":48,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Satelight","count":33,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":31,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":25,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"科普","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2026","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美食","count":19,"total_c